        <updateDate>2021-02-26T17:31:56Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This resolution expresses the Senate's stance in solidarity with the members of the San Isidro Movement, an organization of artists, activists, academics, and journalists protesting increased censorship and persecution in Cuba. Further, it calls on Cuba to release arbitrarily imprisoned artists and journalists, repeal laws that violate freedom of expression, and engage with activists seeking to advance freedom of expression in Cuba.</p>]]>
        </text>
